  "text": "With the variety of different information types that can serve for inputs into data models, data mining and analysis will be able to identify those with the largest effects on performance, adaptation, fatigue and injury risks, allowing for a more targeted approach to be taken to data collection if required. Furthermore, the integration of current technologies, such as urinary and salivary biomarkers [CITATION_1] , along with more standard physiological assessments, will likely enhance the predictive accuracy of these models.",
